 <subsection xml:id="Question_3_3_9">
    <title> Problem 9</title>
    <ol marker="(a)">
        <li>
            <p>
                Write down a few examples. One of the three numbers in the list must <em>always</em> be divisible by a particular number. Prove it.
            </p>
        </li>
